name: Jazzina Animation Library
tagline: Simple and small CSS animation code for your HTML
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
Jazzina Animation Library is a CSS Library or a .css file that contain CSS code of different animations. These animation can used in your HTML file. It is a simple, fast and small size animation library. You just have to put required animation class in your code and have to link **jazzina.css** in your head section.
`<head>
		<title>Jazzina Animation Library - JAL Sample</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="jazzina.css">
</head>`


***

### Project Name
Jazzina name will be taken from my daughter name **Jaseena Umair**. Just start making this Library and make a name.
